    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "Coding agents are about to stop acting like isolated tools.\n\nHivemind gives your whole team one shared learning layer.\n\nOne agent figures out your codebase, patterns, fixes, and workflows. Then every other agent gets sharper from it.\n\nThat’s the real AI dev team unlock.",
