    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "The next AI gold rush isn’t images or video. It’s 3D assets.\n\nYou can already generate pretty pictures.\nYou can already fake cinematic clips.\n\nBut usable 3D models?\n\nThat’s where the workflow still breaks for most creators.\n\nTripo is quietly fixing that:\n\nimage → multi-view → https://t.co/YfppFiB8CW",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2064074027388531106",
    "time": "2026-06-09 03:56",
    "created_at": "Mon Jun 08 19:56:11 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2064074027388531106",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "And yes, Tripo’s 1st Anniversary Special is live 🎂\n\nUse my invite link and you get 500 bonus credits 👇\n\nNew users can try Pro for $9.9 for the first month, and heavier 3D workflows can get $45 off Max for the first month.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2064074039765938591",
    "time": "2026-06-09 03:56",
    "created_at": "Mon Jun 08 19:56:14 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2064074039765938591",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "Here’s the nasty part:\n\nI can start with Image Generation to create/edit the reference, then use single-image → multi-view so Tripo builds extra angles instead of guessing from one flat photo.\n\nThat matters for harder shapes: hands, props, mechanical parts, weird silhouettes. https://t.co/y4ILtvCrRR",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2064074121563324879",
    "time": "2026-06-09 03:56",
    "created_at": "Mon Jun 08 19:56:33 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2064074121563324879",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "Then I’d run two routes:\n\nSmart Mesh\nFast low-poly base mesh in seconds for games, web, quick iteration.\n\nHD Model 3.1\nHigher-detail model with cleaner topology for Blender, Unity, Unreal, printing, or hero assets.\n\nNot magic. Just way less friction. https://t.co/hNGBl1a9Ec",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2064074197991821602",
    "time": "2026-06-09 03:56",
    "created_at": "Mon Jun 08 19:56:52 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2064074197991821602",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "Then I’d use Seg Mode.\n\nUpload the asset.\n\nSplit it into clean, usable parts.\n\nShow the exact segment you want instead of fighting the whole model.\n\nFor creators, this is where 3D stops feeling like a black box. https://t.co/ccWErMlYIK",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2064074263167221867",
    "time": "2026-06-09 03:57",
    "created_at": "Mon Jun 08 19:57:07 +0000 2026",
