    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "AI won’t replace good 3D artists.\n\nBut it absolutely destroys the boring “blank canvas → first usable asset” stage.\n\nTry Tripo here:\nhttps://t.co/PFKGuOVnIS\n\nInvite code: QIFYxS\n500 bonus credits included.\n\nPro is $9.9 first month. Max gets $45 off first month.\n\nFollow @tripoai",
